	   <tr><td colspan=2>I just completed this quest and wanted to give suggestions for completion.&nbsp;&nbsp;The items are as listed on the mobs that have been posted both in this forum and through this website.  The Coldain Missionaries do drop the Coldain Fetish.  My recomendation is to get all of the other peices of this quest and then see if a high lvl friend of yours will come and help do this last part.  Someone that does not mind the faction hit.  The other three items were easy enough to get.  I will say that the witchdoctor part of it was not hard at all for me...took two trips clearing out all of them to get the idol of woven grass, but they are easy to kill for 37 cleric soloing.  The missionaries however did con red to me, so be careful with this part.  hope this helps, let me know if I can assist you further with info on this quest.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
